#                        Node CLI argv parser used by @jimp/cli)
#
# Available image manipulation actions (loaded onto `jimp.prototype` and
# dynamically enumerated by the CLI at `read --actions` describe time):
# `greyscale` / `invert` / `flip` / `mirror` / `gaussian` / `blur` /
