#                                     the jimp-dev collective; pure-JS
#                                     readers and writers for PNG / JPEG
#                                     / GIF / BMP / TIFF with zero
#                                     external or native dependencies
#                                     (project tagline).  THE answer to
#                                     "I want image manipulation in
#                                     Node without dragging in libvips/
#                                     libjpeg-turbo system C libraries."
#                 → jimp (@jimp/cli — Oliver Moran + jimp-dev — official
#                          command-line wrapper around the jimp library;
#                          read|create|distance|diff subcommands + 8
#                          dynamically-added static-helper commands —
#                          rgbaToInt / intToRGBA / cssColorToHex /
#                          limit255 / compareHashes / colorDiff /
